  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AuthServiceImpl
    Implementation of the AuthService interface, providing methods for registering and updating consumers and wholesalers through the RegistrationFactory and AuthRepository.
    CartServiceImpl
    Implementation of the CartService interface that handles operations related to shopping cart functionality.
    ConsumerAccountServiceImpl
    Implementation of the ConsumerAccountService interface, providing methods to manage consumer accounts such as the retrieval, creation, and updating of consumer account (payment) details.
    ConsumerAddressServiceImpl
    Implementation of the ConsumerAddressService interface, providing methods to manage consumer addresses.
    ConsumerServiceImpl
    Implementation of the ConsumerService interface, providing methods to manage consumer details.
    CurrencyServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the CurrencyService interface that provides methods for retrieving currency exchange rates and converting prices on the wholesaler's end based on the exchange rates and their preferred currency.
    OneMapServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the OneMapService interface, and it interacts with the OneMap API to provide functionalities such as retrieving coordinates from a postal code and calculating the driving time between two sets of coordinates (consumer and wholesaler locations).
    OrderHistoryServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the OrderHistoryService interface and provides methods for retrieving and managing order history for consumer.
    ProductServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the ProductService interface and provides various methods for managing products being sold on ShopPeas such as retrieving product details, adding new products, updating existing products, and fetching product images.
    TransactionCacheServiceImpl
    Handles operations related to transaction cache functionality.
    TransactionsServiceImpl
